\c 3  
\s1 Don’t argue with each other  
\p
\v 1 \w Now|strong="G3756"\w* listen, \w my|strong="G1722"\w* Christian friends, \w when|strong="G5613"\w* \w I|strong="G2504"\w* \w was|strong="G2980"\w* \w there|strong="G1722"\w* \w with|strong="G1722"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w*, \w you|strong="G5210"\w* started \w to|strong="G1410"\w* believe \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G3756"\w*, but \w you|strong="G5210"\w* didn’t understand \w a|strong="G5613"\w* lot \w about|strong="G5613"\w* \w him|strong="G1722"\w*, \w and|strong="G5547"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* didn’t let \w the|strong="G1722"\w* Holy Spirit control \w you|strong="G5210"\w*. \w You|strong="G5210"\w* still let \w your|strong="G1722"\w* old \w human|strong="G4560"\w* spirits control \w you|strong="G5210"\w*. \w You|strong="G5210"\w* \w were|strong="G5613"\w* \w just|strong="G5613"\w* \w like|strong="G5613"\w* babies \w that|strong="G1722"\w* don’t understand \w things|strong="G4152"\w*.  
\v 2 \w You|strong="G5210"\w* \w know|strong="G3568"\w*, babies \w can|strong="G1410"\w*’t eat hard \w food|strong="G1033"\w*. \w They|strong="G1063"\w* \w can|strong="G1410"\w* \w only|strong="G3756"\w* \w drink|strong="G4222"\w* \w milk|strong="G1051"\w*. \w Well|strong="G1063"\w*, \w that|strong="G3756"\w* \w is|strong="G3756"\w* \w a|strong="G3756"\w* picture \w of|strong="G1063"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* mob. \w I|strong="G1063"\w* couldn’t teach \w you|strong="G5210"\w* hard things. \w You|strong="G5210"\w* couldn’t \w understand|strong="G3761"\w* \w them|strong="G3756"\w*. \w And|strong="G3761"\w* \w even|strong="G3761"\w* \w now|strong="G3568"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w are|strong="G3568"\w* \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w ready|strong="G1410"\w* \w to|strong="G1410"\w* listen \w to|strong="G1410"\w* \w me|strong="G4222"\w*.\x * \xo 3:2 \xt Hebrews 5:12-13\x*  
\v 3 \w Even|strong="G2532"\w* \w though|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* Christians \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w still|strong="G2089"\w* don’t \w live|strong="G4043"\w* \w like|strong="G2596"\w* Christians. \w You|strong="G5210"\w* \w still|strong="G2089"\w* \w let|strong="G1510"\w* \w your|strong="G2532"\w* \w old|strong="G2532"\w* \w human|strong="G4559"\w* spirits control \w you|strong="G5210"\w*. \w You|strong="G5210"\w* want \w things|strong="G4559"\w* \w that|strong="G2532"\w* \w other|strong="G1722"\w* \w people|strong="G1510"\w* \w have|strong="G2532"\w*. \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* argue \w with|strong="G1722"\w* \w each|strong="G2596"\w* \w other|strong="G1722"\w*. \w That|strong="G2532"\w* shows \w that|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* letting \w your|strong="G2532"\w* \w human|strong="G4559"\w* spirits control \w you|strong="G5210"\w*, \w not|strong="G3780"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* Holy Spirit. \w You|strong="G5210"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* \w still|strong="G2089"\w* \w like|strong="G2596"\w* \w people|strong="G1510"\w* \w that|strong="G2532"\w* don’t \w know|strong="G1722"\w* \w God|strong="G2532"\w*.  
\v 4 \w You|strong="G3752"\w* see, \w some|strong="G5100"\w* \w of|strong="G5100"\w* \w you|strong="G3752"\w* \w say|strong="G3004"\w*, “\w Paul|strong="G3972"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w our|strong="G1510"\w* leader,” \w and|strong="G1161"\w* \w others|strong="G2087"\w* \w say|strong="G3004"\w*, “\w No|strong="G3756"\w*, \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w Paul|strong="G3972"\w*, Apollos \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w our|strong="G1510"\w* leader.” \w And|strong="G1161"\w* \w you|strong="G3752"\w* argue \w with|strong="G3756"\w* each \w other|strong="G2087"\w*. \w You|strong="G3752"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* just like \w the|strong="G1161"\w* \w people|strong="G1510"\w* \w of|strong="G5100"\w* \w the|strong="G1161"\w* world, \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w God|strong="G3004"\w*’s \w people|strong="G1510"\w*.\x * \xo 3:4 \xt 1 Corinthians 1:12\x*   
\s1 Paul and Apollos worked together for God  
\p
\v 5-8 Just think about Apollos and me, Paul. We are not important bosses. We are only workers for God. God gave each of us our jobs, and we helped you believe in Jesus Christ.  
\p I’ll use picture talk now. Think about a garden. One worker plants seeds, and another worker puts water on the young plants to help them grow properly. But it is God that makes the seeds grow up to be big plants. The worker that plants the seeds is not important, and the worker that gives water to the plants is not important. The important one is God. He makes the plants grow. Well, that picture story about a garden is a picture of you mob. God is making you grow like he makes those plants grow. And Apollos and me, we work in God’s team, just like those workers in that garden. I started telling you about Jesus, and Apollos taught you more about him. We both want you to have life, but we can’t give you new life. God is the one that gives you new life. We are just his workers, and you know, God will pay each of us for our work.\x * \xo 3:5-8 \xt Acts 18:4-11, 24-28\x* \fig One worker plants seeds|src="Planting seeds.tif" size="col" ref="3:5-8" \fig*\fig Another worker waters the plants|src="Watering.tif" size="col" ref="3:5-8" \fig*\fig It is God that makes the plants grow|src="God Causes Growth Field.tif" size="col" ref="3:5-8" \fig*  
\v 9 \w We|strong="G1063"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* like 2 men \w that|strong="G2316"\w* work \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w in|strong="G2316"\w* \w his|strong="G2316"\w* garden, \w and|strong="G2316"\w* \w you|strong="G1510"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* like \w God|strong="G2316"\w*’s garden.  
\s1 Christians \w are|strong="G1510"\w* like \w God|strong="G2316"\w*’s house  
\p \w And|strong="G2316"\w* \w I|strong="G1063"\w*’ll use another picture story. \w This|strong="G1063"\w* picture story shows \w that|strong="G2316"\w* \w you|strong="G1510"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* like \w God|strong="G2316"\w*’s house \w that|strong="G2316"\w* \w he|strong="G1063"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w building|strong="G3619"\w* \w for|strong="G1063"\w* himself.  
\v 10-11 This is the picture story. One builder starts to build a house. First, he puts cement down on the ground for the building to stand on. That cement is called the \em foundation\em*. Then other builders build the house on that cement foundation. This story is a picture of you getting into God’s family. God was good to me and gave me the power to work for him. I told you about Jesus, and it is like I put down a good foundation for you at that time. And now other Christian workers are teaching you more about Jesus. They are like the builders that build on that foundation. They have to do it properly. Jesus is the only strong foundation. Nobody can put down any other foundation for God’s family.   
\p
\v 12 \w I|strong="G1161"\w*’ll tell \w you|strong="G1487"\w* \w more|strong="G1161"\w* \w of|strong="G1909"\w* \w this|strong="G3588"\w* picture story \w about|strong="G1909"\w* \w the|strong="G1161"\w* builders. \w Good|strong="G3588"\w* builders \w build|strong="G2026"\w* \w with|strong="G1909"\w* really \w good|strong="G3588"\w* \w things|strong="G3588"\w* like \w gold|strong="G5553"\w*, \w or|strong="G1161"\w* silver, \w or|strong="G1161"\w* jewels. \w But|strong="G1161"\w* \w other|strong="G1161"\w* builders don’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* work properly, \w they|strong="G1161"\w* don’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* care, \w they|strong="G1161"\w* \w only|strong="G1487"\w* \w use|strong="G3588"\w* \w wood|strong="G3586"\w*, \w or|strong="G1161"\w* \w grass|strong="G5528"\w*, \w or|strong="G1161"\w* leaves. \w If|strong="G1487"\w* \w a|strong="G1909"\w* fire comes, \w the|strong="G1161"\w* parts \w of|strong="G1909"\w* \w the|strong="G1161"\w* house \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w are|strong="G3588"\w* \w made|strong="G1161"\w* \w of|strong="G1909"\w* \w wood|strong="G3586"\w*, \w or|strong="G1161"\w* \w grass|strong="G5528"\w*, \w or|strong="G1161"\w* leaves, \w those|strong="G3588"\w* parts \w will|strong="G5100"\w* burn \w up|strong="G2026"\w*. \w But|strong="G1161"\w* \w the|strong="G1161"\w* parts \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w are|strong="G3588"\w* \w made|strong="G1161"\w* \w of|strong="G1909"\w* \w gold|strong="G5553"\w*, \w or|strong="G1161"\w* silver, \w or|strong="G1161"\w* jewels, \w those|strong="G3588"\w* parts \w will|strong="G5100"\w* stay \w good|strong="G3588"\w*. \w So|strong="G1161"\w* \w you|strong="G1487"\w* can know \w which|strong="G3588"\w* builders \w did|strong="G5100"\w* \w a|strong="G1909"\w* \w good|strong="G3588"\w* job. Christian workers \w are|strong="G3588"\w* like \w those|strong="G3588"\w* builders \w in|strong="G1909"\w* \w the|strong="G1161"\w* picture story. \w Some|strong="G5100"\w* Christian workers \w do|strong="G3588"\w* \w a|strong="G190